added.title: Paint That a Shame
added.description: Leshawna creates a paint balloon fight to decide who gets to come with her to an amusement park.

added.title: Snots Landing
added.description: Beth gets Courtney's diorama furniture stuck up her nose and Courtney needs it back before the diorama contest judge arrives.

added.title: I Am My Mom
added.description: Steven struggles to fix his mistakes.

added.title: Kiki's Pizza Delivery Service
added.description: Steven saves Kiki from some delicious nightmares.

added.title: Steven vs. Amethyst
added.description: Steven and Amethyst get competitive while training with Pearl.

added.title: Beta
added.description: Steven and Amethyst visit some friends in the country but Amethyst isn't being herself.

added.title: Say Uncle
added.description: A long lost relative of Steven's comes to town to aid him in unlocking the power of his mother's Gem!

added.title: Sworn to the Sword
added.description: Connie trains with Pearl to be a swordfighter.

added.title: Rising Tides/Crashing Skies
added.description: Ronaldo does some investigative reporting on whether Steven and the Crystal Gems are safe for Beach City.

added.title: Warp Tour
added.description: Steven thinks he sees something creepy traversing the warp streams and the Gems try to ease his paranoia.

added.title: On the Run
added.description: Steven and Amethyst try out life on the road.

added.title: Winter Forecast
added.description: Steven has to get Connie home before it snows.

added.title: Hedgehog Werewolf
added.description: Hedgehog gets bit by a cute puppy and is starting to act strange.

added.title: Mr. Softball
added.description: Susie challenges the campers to a game of softball to get out of doing a chore.

added.title: Babysitting Bedlam/Rubbed the Wrong Way
added.description: Rubbed the Wrong Way: After a Bakugan field errupts the town kids stampede to get their own Bakugan but when the field is contaminated Lia must save the day./Babysitting Bedlam: Dan and Wynton meet a strange boy who leads them into an underground maze where they discover the boy's Bakugan has been enslaved.

added.title: The Wild Hunt
added.description: A fierce creature is terrorizing the Candy Kingdom but before Finn can slay the beast, he must first overcome a guilty conscience.

added.title: The First Investigation
added.description: Finn and Jake are tasked with investigating reports of a haunting at Joshua and Margaret's old office.

added.title: Temple of Mars
added.description: Searching for answers on Mars, Finn and Jermaine discover that they must first survive a cunning Martian mental trap.

added.title: Lady Rainicorn of the Crystal Dimension
added.description: Jake's son TV finds a hidden box and draws the attention of a super cool Rainicorn named Lee.

added.title: Cherry Cream Soda
added.description: With the arrival of an impossible visitor, Cherry Cream Soda's life is thrown into disarray.

added.title: Finn the Human
added.description: After chasing the Lich through the portal, Finn and Jake meet a wishmaster named Prismo.

added.title: Conquest of Cuteness
added.description: King Snuggadoodle and the Huggaboopies invade Finn and Jake's tree house.

added.title: Loyalty to the King
added.description: There's a new "Nice King" in Ooo, and he looks kinda like someone else we know.

added.title: Slumber Party Panic
added.description: Finn must keep his promise to Princess Bubblegum and cover up the zombie problem they've created.

added.title: Trouble in Lumpy Space
added.description: Finn and Jake try to go on a quest while protecting Tree Trunks.

added.title: Merry Christmas
added.description: When the Rustbucket's A/C goes on the fritz in the middle of the desert, Ben, Max and Gwen take refuge at Holiday Village, an over the top Christmas theme park that seems to appear out of nowhere. The place is run by an evil entity known as Mr. Jingles, who takes Max prisoner because he believes Max is Santa! It's up to Ben and Gwen to free Max and break the spell Mr. Jingles has cast on Holiday Village, freeing others who've been trapped their for years and releasing the theme park.

added.title: Back with a Vengeance
added.description: Ben's feeling cocky with the watch. He's unlocked its secret, and now can become any alien he wants, whenever he wants. That's the good news. The bad news is, after finding one another in the depths of space, Kevin 11 and Vilgax have teamed up and have returned to earth to destroy Ben and get the Omnitrix.

added.title: The More Things Change Part 1
added.description: Now on his own, Ben sets out to be a solo superhero, with new alien heroes at his disposal, but Grandpa Max has other plans. (Introducing Rook, Malware, Khyber, Nemetrix alien Crabdozer, new Ben aliens Feedback & Blox, Pakmar.)

added.title: A Jolt from the Past
added.description: Alien pests from Ben's youth come back, but now they need Ben's help. (Introducing Fistrick, & new Ben alien Gravattack.)

added.title: Trouble Helix
added.description: Flashback episode: Young Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max visit Azmuth on Galvan Prime. There, they have their first encounter with Malware, a corrupted Mechamorph who's determined to make Azmuth cure him, by any means!

added.title: Have I Got a Deal for You
added.description: Ben and Rook must stop a giant rampaging alien from destroying Bellwood while dealing with a peace-loving alien-rights activist who doesn't want it hurt. (Introducing Hokestar, Solid Plugg 1st appearance, Pax, Sunder.)

added.title: It Was Them
added.description: Dr. Animo has escaped his Plumber prison, and Ben and Rook must track him down before he turns the world into his personal mutant ant farm! (Introducing Nemetrix alien Slamworm, Galvan Plumbers Blukic and Driba, Arctiguana, new Ben alien Crashhopper.)

added.title: So Long, and Thanks for All the Smoothies
added.description: When Ben and Rook investigate a mysterious alien ghost ship, they discover that Argit and the Vreedle Brothers are fighting for possession of a doomsday device! (Introducing Solid Plugg.)

added.title: Hot Stretch
added.description: Ben and Rook encounter a race of elastic, hot-blooded aliens in Undertown who want to use a stolen nuclear fusion engine to activate a volcano! (Introducing Ester, Seebik & the Kraaho.)

added.title: Of Predators and Prey Part 1
added.description: After a heated argument, Ben and Rook go their separate ways, giving Khyber the Huntsman his best chance to capture Ben! (Introducing Dr. Psychobos, new Nemetrix aliens Mucillator & Terroranchula; new Ben alien Ballweevil.)

added.title: Outbreak
added.description: When Dr. Psychobos steals a part out of the Omnitrix, causing chaotic side effects, it's up to Ben, Rook, and a small team of Plumbers get everything back to normal. (Introducing new Ben alien Kickin' Hawk, temp Ben alien Walkatrout, Upchuck Rook.)

added.title: Secrets
added.description: Grandpa Max's mysterious past comes to light when Vilgax shows up on earth in search of the Omnitrix. And the family must work together to defeat him.
